address: Xã An Mỹ, Huyện Quỳnh Phụ, Tỉnh Thái Bình
thought:
**Determining the New Administrative Unit for "Xã An Mỹ"**

Okay, so the user wants to know the current administrative location for "Xã An Mỹ, Huyện Quỳnh Phụ, Tỉnh Thái Bình." My thought process is pretty straightforward here. First, I need to understand if the province has changed.  I quickly checked for province mergers, and yep, "Tỉnh Thái Bình" has become part of "Tỉnh Hưng Yên" according to document "60-NQ/TW".

Next, I have to dig into the resolutions to see what happened to "Xã An Mỹ" within "Huyện Quỳnh Phụ".  I scanned the relevant resolutions, particularly focusing on those mentioning "An Mỹ" and "Quỳnh Phụ."  Bingo!  Resolution "1666/NQ-UBTVQH15" is key.  It explicitly states that "Xã An Mỹ" was merged along with several others to form the new unit, "Xã Phụ Dực".

So, that's the mapping: "Xã An Mỹ" from "Tỉnh Thái Bình" (now "Tỉnh Hưng Yên") is now part of the new ward, "Xã Phụ Dực." To confirm, I checked the known "New wards" list for "Xã Phụ Dực" in "Tỉnh Hưng Yên," and it's there with code "12523".

The resolution is pretty clear-cut, the mapping is explicit, so my confidence in this identification is quite high.
